reviewText: This was a gift for my parents and the LOVE it!
This DVD is interesting if you like architecture, the sites chosen were good, but I would have liked more of them. But then I can't get enough of a good thing.
a few of the shows are a bit dated, but most have lots of interesting material
My husband and I love history channel documentaries and this one was great!!!!!!! We liked every episode. Good price too.
